---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — BYD Finder" description="About BYD Finder, an independent BYD Canada news and reviews site.">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 py-12 md:py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--color-ink)]">About</h1>
    <div class="prose-article mt-6">
      <p>
        BYD Finder is an independent enthusiast publication tracking BYD's entry
        into the Canadian EV market. We aggregate trusted reporting, curate
        video reviews, and maintain living pages for each model headed to
        Canadian roads.
      </p>
      <p>
        We are not affiliated with BYD. Some outbound links may be affiliate
        partnerships &mdash; these never influence which stories we cover or
        which reviews we feature.
      </p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Story tips, corrections, partnerships: <a href="/ca/contact">contact us</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
